==Sequel== {{main|Kadavul 2}} In January 2018, Prabhakaran announced that he would be making a sequel to the film.<ref>https://www.behindwoods.com/tamil-movies-cinema-news-16/bharathirajas-kadavul-2-co-starring-seeman-with-music-by-ilayaraja-launch-on-jan-18.html</ref> The film has RR Tami Selvan, Swathy as the lead pair with Imman Annachi and veteran Seetha essaying crucial roles.<ref>https://www.deccanchronicle.com/entertainment/kollywood/020119/kadavul-2-coming-soon.html</ref>
